)
</bibRefCitation>
, Thomasville, 
<collectingCountry id="47FB763BFF97FFD9D6653CC29A03E5D7" box="[1025,1119,1164,1190]" name="Georgia" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Georgia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="5B7D4B5AFF97FFD9D6EF3CC29B74E5D7" author="Fattig" box="[1163,1320,1164,1190]" pageId="24" pageNumber="28" refString="Fattig, P. W. (1949) The Carabidae or ground beetles of Georgia. Emory University Museum Bulletin 7, 62 pp." type="book" year="1949">
