)
</bibRefCitation>
. The Fattig collection, now housed in the University of 
<collectingCountry id="47FB763BFF97FFD9D3CA3C929C53E587" box="[430,527,1244,1270]" name="Georgia" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Georgia</collectingCountry>
, does not contain any specimens identified under that name (Cecil Smith, personal communication). I have seen one specimen in 
